<tr class="row">
<td class="body" valign="top">
<table border="0" height="100" width="100%" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="2">
<tr>
<td valign="top"><font class="body">A tale of determination, patience, perseverance, and the good old British Bulldog Spirit.<p>Aegis of Life - Paladin, Cleric only Off Hand, Back<br>AC12, 10Wis, 25sv Disease, Heavy<br>1 Shot Superior Heal<p>OK I hear you say So what I got better. Well the item is good but getting it is what its all about. You need Allied plus with Clerics in Qeynos to even get the Quest and higher to hand in the items.<p>I started working on Faction in my mid 20&#39s bone chips by the stack, bandit sashes by the Backpack and only when I had finally gotten high enough to get the Quest did I start to look for Lord Grimrot.<p>Ahh yes Lord Grimrot he is to be found in South Karana just South of the Zone to Noreth Karana in an Undead Camp. He has to be killed twice and you need to loot a NO DROP Scythe, and a NO DROP Heart easy enough you say well yes anyone can loot but try get Grimrot to Spawn that is the fun!!!<p>He is on a 3 hours 20 mins spawn and has a PH and after 4PH&#39s I was getting to the stage of giving up and looking for a better Cloak, but No I decided to try again, so once again set up camp slaughtered Skeletons by the graveyard and finally after almost 3 hours of waiting he popped.<p>Ooh I think which one is it? Undead or Live Grimrot (Undead soloable by mid to high 20&#39s Live Hard for a mid 40&#39s)<p>Yes Gena&#39s luck is in its the Live one !!!  Buffs up and pulls, Ouch hit for almost 400 harmtouch then the battle begins he has Very High MR so I know its a fight to the death as cant root and run (hmm Paladins don&#39t run) Thankfully over the past few days I have been lucky enough to be in the company of Galathiel Auctioning her wares, when Deepwater has pooped for sale so in my new armour I am whacking this evil SK Hehe he is missing our lives are dropping at a similar rate then he misses just too many times and I don&#39t.  &quot;You have killed Lord Grimrot&quot; Exp and Faction and a NO DROP Sycthe.<p>Normally I would have to wait again for the Undead Grimrot but my luck is indead in Akkanar has a NO DROP Heart and also the required Faction so with a short foray into West Karana for some more Bandit Sashes we head for Qeynos.  More bonechips handed in more Sashes handed in we try the Quest and WOOOOOT!!! I got my Aegis.<p>I know a long story but its a Loooooong Quest, my heartfelt thanks to Akkanar for the Heart and Galathiel for the Company. You 2 are what it is to be KoR.<p>I salute you both.
<!-- SIGNATURE -->
<hr>
Love and Kisses<p>Genadine Soultaker<br>Paladin of 47 Hard Fought Battles<br>Follower of Mithanial Marr
<!-- SIGNATURE --></font></td>
</tr>
